{"tid":2097757,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"國安公署臨時基地曝光！","createTime":"2020-07-07T04:38:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T04:43:18.000Z","uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d6f033ef5f02112b14882d627dc3f8fbda600cb6","tid":2097757,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:38:25.000Z","msg":"《港區國安法》本月1日正式生效，隨着國務院日前（3日）宣佈任命駐港國安公署署長人選，公署的硬件亦曝光，有周刊爆出中央駐港「第四機構」國安公署將以銅鑼灣維景酒店作為臨時基地。今日早上，銅鑼灣維景酒店門口有大批軍裝警員戒備，大堂玻璃門已用圍板圍封，有工人在外牆進行維修。《蘋果》致電酒店查詢預訂房間事宜，前台職員稱酒店近期正進行維修，至少半年不會接收客人。記者今晨所見，該酒店已不見有住客，工人忙於作維修及裝修，更有2、30名軍裝警員在場戒備，保安員更質疑前來了解的區議員「是否想踩國家法」，氣氛緊張。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OO3YWG3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOO3YWG3.png&h=2fce1b6b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R4xnDVp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR4xnDVp.png&h=332b70cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200707&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=61138931\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200707%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D61138931&d=uYDAXyhVPN7xTSuHIXBXElScv4UPbHgCWRxxYzHlmUY%3D&h=dd8e2ba1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200707%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D61138931&h=6d9ec8ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200707&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=61138931</a>"},{"pid":"eb1d686577ac262771b782e41adae2d2649f47af","tid":2097757,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:39:47.000Z","msg":"「保安員」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83240af19f65d564be6a2b4fb37126afc52241c9","tid":2097757,"uid":308264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:40:58.000Z","msg":"有冇手足扮工人入去放cam<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1